tool_description: View OOKLA speed test results in mobile and fixed domain for cities and regions around the world. Updated monthly based on millions of speed tests performed by consumers.
name: Data Speedtest
title: Data Speedtest

api_list.name: Download Speeds per Area/Provider for Speed Tests in Mobile Domain v2
api_list.description: View the download speeds (25th, 50th, 75th percentile) , upload speeds (50th percentile) and latency (ms) of providers in each country/area for which data speed tests exist in mobile domain.

api_list.name: Time Periods per Area for Speed Tests in Mobile Domain v2
api_list.description: View the time periods (quarters of year) in each country/area for which data speed tests exist in mobile domain.

api_list.name: Data Providers per Area for Speed Tests in Mobile Domain v2
api_list.description: View the data providers in each country/area for which data speed tests exist in mobile domain.

api_list.name: Areas per Country for Speed Tests in Mobile Domain v2
api_list.description: View the areas in each country for which data speed tests exist in mobile domain.

api_list.name: Countries for Speed Tests in Mobile Domain v2
api_list.description: View countries for which data speed tests exist in mobile domain.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://data-speedtest.p.rapidapi.com/mobile/v2/countries/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "data-speedtest.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
